  * etc/xdg/xdg-xubuntu/xfce4/xfconf/…/xfce4-session.xml:
    - enable support of GNOME services for smooth integration with
      gnome-keyring. lp: #1008993
    - replace xfce4-settings-helper with xfsettingsd.

